The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Nation | Blood scam 
                                                                                                               Blood scam 
                            
	Jaipur, Aug. 30 (PTI): A laboratory owner has been arrested for allegedly collecting blood from donors without proper tests and supplying it to a nursing home in Rajasthans Sriganganagar district.        
	The government has ordered a probe amid charges that the blood was HIV-infected.         
	The laboratorys owner, Hetram Goyal, was arrested yesterday while the nursing home owner is on the run, the police said.                                                                                                                                                                            
